1b:[["$","span",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"Product overview"}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"What Are Our Ashwagandha KSM-66 Tablets?"}],[["$","p","Feeling mentally cluttered and overwhelmed? Ashwagandha has been a trusted solution in Ayurvedic and Unani traditions for centuries, thanks to its adaptogenic properties that help support calm, clarity, and focus during busy or stressful moments.",{"children":"Feeling mentally cluttered and overwhelmed? Ashwagandha has been a trusted solution in Ayurvedic and Unani traditions for centuries, thanks to its adaptogenic properties that help support calm, clarity, and focus during busy or stressful moments."}],["$","p","That’s exactly why we’ve created our Ashwagandha Tablets – a handy way to enjoy the benefits of this powerful herb without having to deal with its naturally bitter taste!",{"children":"That’s exactly why we’ve created our Ashwagandha Tablets – a handy way to enjoy the benefits of this powerful herb without having to deal with its naturally bitter taste!"}],["$","p","Unlike regular ashwagandha supplements, ours deliver a potent 1500mg of high-absorbing ashwagandha KSM-66 , all in a vegan-friendly formula. With 180 tablets in every bottle, you’ll be covered for a full six months without frequent reorders .",{"children":"Unlike regular ashwagandha supplements, ours deliver a potent 1500mg of high-absorbing ashwagandha KSM-66 , all in a vegan-friendly formula. With 180 tablets in every bottle, you’ll be covered for a full six months without frequent reorders ."}]]]
